  Security bump. Apply upstream patch from
  https://bugzilla.redhat.com/attachment.cgi?id=405473 wrt bug 324017.

  24 Feb 2013; Christoph Junghans <ottxor@gentoo.org>
  nss-db-2.2.3_pre1-r2.ebuild, nss-db-2.2.3_pre1-r3.ebuild:
  dropped gawk from deps as it is in system set (bug #455686)

  03 May 2012; Robin H. Johnson <robbat2@gentoo.org> nss-db-2.2-r1.ebuild,
  nss-db-2.2.3_pre1-r2.ebuild, nss-db-2.2.3_pre1-r3.ebuild:
  New glibc now includes nss-db again, so block the new glibc here, and block
  nss-db in new glibc

